  "detailed_description": "<i>Dr. Atominus</i> is a short platformer with metroidvania elements and a cool sci-fi story.<br><br>Doctor Atominus finally succeeds to magnify an atom. But the atom is alive and it escapes! Play as the atom who wants to escape from the experiments of Dr. Atominus and find out why the scientist needs you so badly.<br><br>Explore the 4th dimension, get unique abilities, and eventually, make the right choices.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 areas to explore<br></li><li>5 bosses<br></li><li>3 different endings<br></li><li>Fun sci-fi story<br></li><li>Good chiptune music</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294750/extras/deb8afbed95b15cf7d599a1ccc0d960d.avif?t=1769351779\" width=141 height=141 /></span>",
